&lt;%var Temp= Interfaces.queryInterface( associationName,
&quot;com.rational.uml70.IUMLAssociation&quot;);
function getuppername()
{
var end1;
var end2;
var NonOwningTemp;
var NonOwningFinal;
end1 = Temp.GetPrimaryAssociationEnd();
end2 = Temp.GetSecondaryAssociationEnd();
if (end1.IsNavigable()) 
{
NonOwningTemp=end1.getName();
}
else 
{
NonOwningTemp=end2.getName();
}
  return NonOwningTemp;
}%&gt;return &lt;%=getuppername()%&gt;;

}
